ios.subtitle: Tap To Become A Rhythm Master

editorialNotes.standard: Sometimes, the best games are the most simple ones. We love Cube Skip because it's devilishly simple: tap left to guide a ball down one stair, tap right for a big, two-stair leap. You just have to keep going. Sounds easy, right? Well, for us it was about as easy as patting our head and rubbing our tummy.
